          <span class="tm-card__piece">Bespoke engagement ring, 18k white gold</span>
        </footer>
      </div>

      <div class="tm-slide">
        <div class="tm-card__quote">&ldquo;</div>
        <blockquote class="tm-card__text">
          I commissioned a necklace for my wife's anniversary. The collaboration was seamless — they translated a rough sketch into something extraordinary. She hasn't taken it off since the day she unwrapped it.
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="tm-card__footer">
          <div class="tm-card__divider"></div>
          <span class="tm-card__name">James T.</span>
          <span class="tm-card__piece">Custom diamond necklace, platinum</span>
