          Honestly wasn't sure about the design fee at first, but it completely makes sense once you're in the process. I had three rounds of revisions and they were patient every single time. The final ring is perfect.
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="tm-card__footer">
          <div class="tm-card__divider"></div>
          <span class="tm-card__name">Daniel K.</span>
          <span class="tm-card__piece">Signet ring, 18k yellow gold</span>
